    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 guidance for Class II device at MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate CFD model predicts hemolysis index within 8.3% mean error across the full operating envelope. Uncertainty quantification on primary validation result confirms RH predictions robust to inlet boundary condition variability. Model is fit for purpose to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device COU.",
